      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age in a few areas. The engine and drivetrain are solid, but you can expect some minor cosmetic wear on the interior and a few scuffs on the exterior paint. It has been regularly serviced, though it may soon require some routine maintenance like new brake pads or tires. This is an honest, functional car perfect for someone looking for a dependable ride without the premium price tag of a newer model.",
