    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my reliable ride. She\u2019s been a total joy to drive and is still in really wonderful shape! While there are a few minor signs of love from over the years, she runs like a dream and has been super well-maintained. This is a perfect, dependable choice for anyone looking for a quality car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today. I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have\u2014feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
