    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2005 Porsche 911 Carrera, a driver-centric 997.1 featuring the 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six. This M96/05 power unit delivers linear torque across the rev range, optimized by VarioCam Plus valve timing. The 6-speed Getrag G97 manual gearbox offers precise gate selection and short throws. Crucially, the IMS bearing has been addressed with a dual-row ceramic retrofit, and the rear main seal is dry. The chassis retains its factory-spec McPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry, providing exceptional lateral grip and communicative steering feedback. While showing minor patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain razor-sharp. A turn-key example for the enthusiast who prioritizes visceral performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean interior. Reliable engine.",
