    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m looking to find a new home for this absolute gem. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride and honestly still looks and drives great! It\u2019s been well-loved and taken care of, so you\u2019re getting a solid car that\u2019s ready for many more adventures. Perfect for someone who wants a quality vehicle without the brand-new price tag. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 29800.0,
