    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sorted 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory-spec variable M differential lock. Critical enthusiast maintenance has been addressed: the rear subframe has been reinforced to mitigate floor cracking, and the dual-VANOS system has been serviced to ensure precise cam timing. The suspension retains its factory geometry with refreshed bushings, providing exceptional lateral stability and communicative steering feedback. While the exterior shows minor stone chips and patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the powertrain remains tight with a linear power delivery up to the 8,000 RPM redline. A turn-key performance icon for the technical driver.",
